{
  "texts": [
    "This is a large-scale egocentric video benchmark recorded by 32 participants in their own kitchens while performing unscripted activities (Damen et al., 2018).",
    "RGB, Audio and Flow data are available in the dataset.",
    "To validate our approach, we use the experimental protocol defined in Munro and Damen (2020).",
    "According to this protocol, (i) we only use the three kitchens with the largest amount of annotated samples (hereafter referred to as D1, D2, and D3) and (ii) we consider only verb classification task and a subset of eight labels.",
    "The challenges lie not only in the large domain shift that exists between the different kitchens, but also in the unbalanced distribution of classes within and between domains."
  ]
}